- comment must describe what the repository does, not why score was assigned
- keep comment simple and practical, no abstract architecture phrases
- verdict: one of weak, fair, good, strong, excellent
- risk_level: one of low, medium, high
- evidence: array of 3 short strings citing concrete signals from the analysis
- Write comment and evidence in language: {{ settings.output_language }}

